#: ../../source/language/python/framework.rst:15
msgid "配置相关"
msgstr "Configuration"

#: ../../source/language/python/framework.rst:16
msgid ""
"Nginx 在为 Django 做反向代理时，静态文件目录配置错误会导致源码泄露。访问 /static.. 会 301 重定向到 "
"/static../"
msgstr ""
"When Nginx acts as a reverse proxy for Django, an incorrect static file "
"directory configuration can disclose source code. Accessing /static.. returns "
"a 301 redirect to /static../."

